The paper discusses the security challenges related to infrastructure in blockchain technology, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also explores the concept of decentralized trusted computing base, which is related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the peer-to-peer network of nodes that make up the blockchain system, which is related to distributed systems (cs.Distributed). Finally, the paper discusses the security and robustness of the blockchain system, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
